<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7909403>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5 Phylogeny of the Hermeuptychia clade and nearby genera based on the FULL dataset. Interpretation of support values can be found in the legend. The scale bars under the butterfly images equal 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7909403/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7968438>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2 Phylogeny of Euptychia based on the FULL dataset. Interpretation of support values can be found in the legend. The scale bars under the butterfly images equal 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7968438/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7909399>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3 Phylogeny of the Cyllopsis clade based on the FULL dataset. Interpretation of support values can be found in the legend. The scale bars under the butterfly images equal 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7909399/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7909429>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14 Saurona triangula comb.n. (a) male wing venation—stippled area on FW shows dorsal androconial scales around vein M2 and ventral androconial scales around vein 2A, androconial hair-like scales at anterior edge discal cell are also indicated; (b and c) male dorsal (b) and ventral (c); (d and e) female dorsal (d) and ventral (e). Scale bars 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7909429/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7909431>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15 Saurona triangulacomb.n. A-F, male genitalia (dissection KW-21-31), lateral tip abdomen (a), lateral (b) with posterior view juxta, dorsal (c), ventral (d), aedeagus lateral (e) and dorsal (f); (g–j), female genitalia (dissection USNM loan 2090579), lateral view exterior tip abdomen (g), ventral view exterior tip abdomen (h), dorsal view interior abdomen (i), corpus bursae perpendicular to signa (j).Scale bars 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7909431/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7909435>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16 Saurona gen.n. Species diversity mapped on a 2 degree grid. Colours ranging from dark green to red represent increasing diversity." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7909435/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

